## Code Example
```javascript
// Pseudo-infra sketch showing hub attachments
const hubVpc = new Vpc('Hub-VPC-RegionA');
const tgw = new TransitGateway('TGW-RegionA');
const dx = new DirectConnect('DX-PrivateVIF');

// Attach tenant VPCs as spokes
tenants.forEach(tenant => {
  new VpcAttachment(tenant.vpc, tgw);
});

// PrivateLink for shared services
new VpcEndpoint('Analytics-API', 'PrivateLink');
```

